2020-04-15}}</ref> first aired in Italy in 2019, Australia in 2020, and in France expected late 2020.)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mondofox.it/guida-tv/foxcrime/2019-10-31/|title=GUIDA TV di FoxCrime di gioved\u00ec 31 ottobre 2019|last=|first=|date=31 October 2019|website=MondoFox|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=14 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=\"Les petits meurtres d'Agatha Christie\" Un cadavre au petit d\u00e9jeuner (TV Episode 2019) - IMDb|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt10269126/releaseinfo|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref><ref name=\"telestar\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.telestar.fr/actu-tv/exclu-telestar-les-petits-meurtres-d-agatha-christie-ce-n-est-pas-fini-467484|title=EXCLU TELESTAR. Les Petits meurtres d'Agatha Christie ce n'est... - T\u00e9l\u00e9 Star|last=Telestar.fr|date=2019-10-28|website=www.telestar.fr|language=fr|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n |LineColor       = \n}}\n}}\n\n== Series Three: 1970s France (announced 2019) ==\nA third series, with a new cast and set in France in the 1970s, was announced in 2019.<ref name=\"telestar\" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.programme.tv/news/series/208867-emotion-dans-greys-anatomy-la-nouvelle-saison-des-petits-meurtres-dagatha-christie-et-les-abdos-de-loup-denis-elion-les-tournages-de-la-semaine-photos/|title=Emotion dans Grey\u2019s Anatomy, la nouvelle saison des Petits Meurtres d\u2019Agatha Christie et les abdos de Loup-Denis Elion\u2026 Les tournages de la semaine (PHOTOS) - series - T\u00e9l\u00e9 2 semaines|website=www.programme.tv/news|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n\n== Notes ==\n\n* A distinct four-part mini-series, \"{{lang|fr|Petits Meurtres en Famille}}\", adapted from ''Hercule Poirot's Christmas'', was released in 2006. Although Larosi\u00e8re and Lampion are the main characters (played by the same actors), this mini-series is not a prequel or sequel to the later series.\n*[[Alexandre Labarthe]], who plays Laurence's son (S2 E10, S2 E22), is Samuel Labarthe's son.{{Citation needed|date=April 2020}}\n*Laurence drives a [[Facel Vega]] Facellia FA red Bordeaux coupe.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lesanciennes.com/annonce/A312537-ventes-auto-facel-vega-facellia-fa-coupe-2-2-1960.html?ftype=&fcat=&search=FACEL%20VEGA|title=V\u00e9hicule du film \"les petits meurtres d'Agatha Christie\"|last=|date=2020-03-08|year=|publisher=|pages=|language=|format=|url-status=|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-09|quote=|periodical=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.facel-vega.asso.fr/tv/tv.html|title=Facel Vega \u00e1 la T\u00e9l\u00e9vision|last=|date=2013-03-29|year=|publisher=|pages=|language=|format=|url-status=|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-09|quote=|periodical=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://au.rrforums.net/forum/messages/16947/22770.html?1479246125|title=RR Forums Australia|last=|date=2016-11-15|year=|publisher=|pages=|language=|format=|url-status=|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-09|quote=|periodical=}}</ref>\n\n== Complete cast ==\n{| class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible mw-collapsed center\" style=\"font-size: 86%; width:60%; left:0 auto; text-align:center;\"\n|+ align=\"center\" colspan=\"4\" |<big>{{nowrap|Cast of Series One and Series Two}}</big>\n|- style=\"background-color: #CCCCFF\" \n|'''Casting'''||'''Character'''||'''Episodes'''|| scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 80px;\" |'''Year'''\n|-\n|[[Antoine Dul\u00e9ry]]\n|Jean Larosi\u00e8re<br />Larosi\u00e8re's nephew\n|11<br />1\n|2009\u20132012&nbsp;<br />2020\n|-\n|[[Marius Colucci]]\n|\u00c9mile Lampion\n|11\n|2009\u20132012\n|-\n|[[Blandine Bellavoir]]\n|Albertine\nAlice Avril\n|1\n27\n|2011\n2013\u20132020\n|-\n|[[Samuel Labarthe]]\n|Swan Laurence\n|27\n|2013\u20132020\n|-\n|[[\u00c9lodie Frenck]]\n|Marl\u00e8ne Leroy\n|27\n|2013\u20132020\n|-\n|[[Dominique Thomas]]\n|Ernest Tricard\n|27\n|2013\u20132020\n|-\n|[[Christophe Piret]]\n|Guillaume Parisot<br />Robert Jourdeuil\n|1<br />2\n|2012<br />2013\n|-\n|[[Fran\u00e7ois Godart]]\n|Robert Jourdeuil\n|15\n|2013\u20132019\n|-\n|[[\u00c9ric Beauchamp]]\n|Martin\n|16\n|2013\u20132018\n|-\n|[[Serge Dubois]]\n|M\u00e9nard\n|9\n|2009\u20132012\n|-\n|[[Olivier Carr\u00e9 (acteur)|Olivier Carr\u00e9]]\n|Verdure<br />Roger Bessan\n|5<br />1\n|2010\u20132012<br />2019\n|-\n|Bubulle\n|Marl\u00e8ne's goldfish Bubulle\n|5\n|2015\u20132020\n|-\n|[[Flore Bonaventura]]<br />[[Alice Isaaz]]\n|Juliette Larosi\u00e8re\n|1<br />1\n|2010<br />2012\n|-\n|[[Anne Beno\u00eet]]\n|Madame Daste<br />Annick Devassene\n|1<br />1\n|2009<br />2015\n|-\n|[[H\u00e9l\u00e8ne Vincent]]\n|Kristin\n|1\n|2009\n|-\n|[[Pascal Elso]]\n|L\u00e9opold Vallabr\u00e8gues\n|1\n|2009\n|-\n|[[Corinne Masiero]]\n|Ang\u00e9lique\n|1\n|2009\n|-\n|[[Denis Lavant]]\n|Andr\u00e9 Custe\n|1\n|2009\n|-\n|[[Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Pierrot]]\n|Jean Villiers\n|1\n|2009\n|-\n|[[Robinson St\u00e9venin]]\n|Jean\n|1\n|2009\n|-\n|[[Fran\u00e7oise Bertin]]\n|Emilie Dubreuil\n|1\n|2009\n|-\n|[[Lannick Gautry]]\n|Mathieu Vidal\n|1\n|2010\n|-\n|[[Isabelle Candelier]]\n|Christine Boisseau\n|1\n|2010\n|-\n|[[Guilaine Londez]]\n|Mademoiselle Thuleau\n|1\n|2010\n|-\n|[[Mata Gabin]]\n|Esm\u00e9ralda\n|1\n|2011\n|-\n|[[Jean-Marie Winling]]\n|Pierre Foug\u00e8res\n|1\n|2012\n|-\n|[[Patrick Descamps]]\n|Chesnais\n|1\n|2012\n|-\n|[[Fran\u00e7oise Fabian]]\n|Alexina Laurence\n|1\n|2013\n|-\n|[[Claude Perron]]\n|Claude Kerrigan\n|1\n|2013\n|-\n|[[Charlie Dupont]]\n|Roland Delavall\u00e9e\n|1\n|2013\n|-\n|[[Isabelle de Hertogh]]\n|Bella Siatidis\n|1\n|2013\n|-\n|[[Dominique Pinon]]\n|Hubert Petitpont\n|1\n|2014\n|-\n|[[Natacha Lindinger]]\n|Euphrasie Maillol\n|4\n|2014\n|-\n|[[Nicolas Vaude]]\n|Stanislas\n|1\n|2014\n|-\n|[[Alban Lenoir]]\n|Paul Coupet\n|1\n|2014\n|-\n|[[Philippe Nahon]]\n|Emile Deboucke\n|1\n|2015\n|-\n|[[Serge Riaboukine]]\n|L\u00e9opold Santini\n|1\n|2015\n|-\n|[[Cyril Guei]]\n|Dr Timoth\u00e9e Glissant\n|13\n|2016\u20132020\n|-\n|[[Sophie Cattani]]\n|Eve Constantin\n|1\n|2016\n|-\n|[[Philippe Rebbot]]\