 Profile Page|url=http://bmg.com/category/music/?artist=versatile|accessdate=14 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130118042749/http://bmg.com/category/music/?artist=versatile|archive-date=18 January 2013|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\nVersatile has produced and remixed for artists like [[Chris Brown (American entertainer)|Chris Brown]], [[Usher (entertainer)|Usher]], [[Fabolous]], [[Jay-Z]], [[Maino]], [[Ciara]], [[Britney Spears]], [[Joe Budden]], [[Slimmie Hendrix|Pittsburgh Slim]], [[Nelly]], [[Nelly Furtado]], amongst others.<ref name=\"redorbit\"/><ref>[http://www.parcitizens.com/2011/04/featurefridays-par-city-featuring.html Parcitizens:  Par-City Featuring Panama - \"Hey, Hey, Hey\" (prod. by Versatile)]</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Versatile- Producer for Fabolous, Method Man, & more|url=http://blog.istandardproducers.com/2009/05/versatile-producer-for-fabolous-method-man-more/|accessdate=14 November 2012|archive-url=https://archive.is/20121211043933/http://blog.istandardproducers.com/2009/05/versatile-producer-for-fabolous-method-man-more/|archive-date=11 December 2012|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n==Selected Discography==\n*2006: [[Method Man]] (feat. [[Redman (rapper)|Redman]]), \"Walk On\"  Def Jam / ''[[4:21... The Day After]]''\n*2007: [[Omillio Sparks]], \"DJ Turn It Up\" Koch/The PayBack\n*2007: [[Fabolous]] feat. [[Jay-Z]], Uncle Murda, \"Brooklyn\" Def Jam / ''[[From Nothin' to Somethin']]'' Def Jam, RIAA Certified Gold Album <ref>{{cite web |title=Fabolous RIAA Gold Album Sales |url=https://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?resultpage=1&table=SEARCH_RESULTS&action=&title=&artist=Fabolous&format=ALBUM&debutLP=&category=&sex=&releaseDate=&requestNo=&type=&level=&label=&company=&certificationDate=&awardDescription=&catalogNo=&aSex=&rec_id=&charField=&gold=&platinum=&multiPlat=&level2=&certDate=&album=&id=&after=&before=&startMonth=1&endMonth=1&startYear=1958&endYear=2007&sort=Artist&perPage=25 |url-status=dead |access-date=2017-08-24 